# Untracked local workspace notes and private docs.
# Exceptions: docs/adr/ (the public Architecture Decision Records) and
# docs/guides/ (the public user guides) ARE tracked — each re-included
# directory is wholly public (see docs/adr/013-public-documentation-layout.md).
# `docs/*` (not `docs/`) keeps the directory itself unexcluded so the
# negations below can re-include them.
.claude/
.agents/
AGENTS.md
CLAUDE.md
docs/*
!docs/adr/
!docs/guides/
